<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٧٨٤]</span> بَكرُ بنُ زُرْعَةَ الخَوْلانِيُّ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سَمِعَ أبا عِنَبَةَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>سَمِعَ مِنْهُ جَرَّاحٌ البَهْرَانِيُّ الشّاميُّ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
